cxxopts
------------------------------------------
Lightweight C++ command line option parser

Runtime requirements:
  pkg-config-1.9.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.40-1
  cmake-3.23.2-1
  cygport-0.36.1-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jarro2783/cxxopts

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jarro2783/cxxopts/archive/refs/tags/v3.1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack cxxopts-3.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./cxxopts-3.1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/cxxopts-3.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/cxxopts-3.1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(cxxopts)
  /usr/include/cxxopts.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/cxxopts/cxxopts-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/cxxopts/cxxopts-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/cxxopts/cxxopts-targets.cmake
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/cxxopts.pc
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/cxxopts.README
  /usr/share/doc/cxxopts/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/cxxopts/README.md

------------------

